cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is about visual recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and the use of learned feature extractors (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper experiments with object detection (cs.MM) and validation on a benchmark dataset (cs.IR).
